tool_name: AI Voice (Text to Speech) with Celebrities
tool_description: Convert any text into hyper realistic voices of celebrities, famous cartoons, and popular culture figures.
title: AI Voice (Text to Speech) with Celebrities

api_list.name: Generate Message
api_list.description: Returns an mp3 url of hyper realistic speech from the celebrity voice_id and text prompt that you pass in.
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://ai-voice-text-to-speech-with-celebrities.p.rapidapi.com/generateMessage"

headers = {
    "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
    "X-RapidAPI-Host": "ai-voice-text-to-speech-with-celebrities.p.rapidapi.com"
}

response = requests.post(url, headers=headers)

print(response.json())

api_list.name: List Voices
api_list.description: Returns a list of famous voices you can use to generate text. The list includes the {voice_id} parameter which will be used in the /generateMessage endpoint to select the voice. The list also contains the speaker/character of the voice.
